Package: libasterix2
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ASTERIX protocol decoder library
 ASTERIX (All Purpose STructured EUROCONTROL Surveillance Information
 EXchange) is a data format used in Air Traffic Management (ATM) for
 exchanging surveillance and other data between ATM systems.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libasterix-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libasterix2 (= ${binary:Version}),
         libexpat1-dev,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: ASTERIX protocol decoder library - development files
 ASTERIX (All Purpose STructured EUROCONTROL Surveillance Information
 EXchange) is a data format used in Air Traffic Management (ATM) for
 exchanging surveillance and other data between ATM systems.
 .
 This package contains the development files (headers, static library).

Package: asterix-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ASTERIX protocol decoder - command-line tools
 ASTERIX (All Purpose STructured EUROCONTROL Surveillance Information
 EXchange) is a data format used in Air Traffic Management (ATM) for
 exchanging surveillance and other data between ATM systems.
 .
 This package contains command-line tools for parsing ASTERIX data from
 files, network streams (multicast), and PCAP captures. Supports output
 in text, JSON, and XML formats.
